Package: agrideshr
Title: Agricultural Experimental Designs in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Evangelos", "Mantzoukas", , "emant@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tutorial package demonstrating the analysis of five classical
    agricultural experimental designs in R: Completely Randomized Design (CRD),
    Randomized Complete Block Design (RCBD), Latin Square Design, Factorial
    Design, and Split-Plot Design. Each design is accompanied by a dataset and
    a detailed vignette covering exploratory analysis, model fitting, assumption
    checking, and post-hoc comparisons.
